description: So I guess the secret's out. My surf buddy Brock Cooper loves jerking off on the beach. We went surfing for a couple of hours and when we were going to head back to our cars Brock told me he was going to hang back and jerk off. I convinced him to wait until I went to my car and got my camera. And the rest of what happen that day is here for all of you to enjoy. Brock Cooper heads back to the beach!
series: Brock Goes Back To The Beach
title: Brock Goes Back To The Beach, Scene #01
